data.description: Welcome home to 13 Pleasant Drive! This beautiful property boasts a covered front porch, offering the perfect spot to enjoy a cup of coffee. Step inside where the interior is all freshly painted. This inviting living room features a stunning stone fireplace, creating a cozy ambiance for those chilly evenings. The heart of this home is the eat-in kitchen, thoughtfully designed with ample cabinet space. Venture downstairs to discover the finished walk-out basement, adorned with wood accent pieces that add a touch of warmth and character along with the sliding barn door that introduces a rustic charm. Embrace the outdoors in your backyard oasis, complete with a stone firepit that beckons for evenings filled with laughter.
